Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:11.15,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}即便天各一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:17.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}即便時光荏苒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:20.65,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}不能忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:24.07,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}無法磨滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:27.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}相擁而泣破涕為笑的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:31.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}與溫存一起留在心頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:34.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}你的擁抱就像魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:37.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}是給予我勇氣的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:44.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}活在夢想凋零的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:50.93,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)}不哀嘆 不彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:57.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}因為我不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:01:00.75,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}無懼挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:04.11,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}不留悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:10.69,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}將率真化作包容與堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:14.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}邁開步伐的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:17.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,100)\pos(960,1060)\k100}駐足停止的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:28.58,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(960,1060)}一定皆是未來的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙萬花筒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,吉特團提供的Yggdrasil（世界樹）一旦投入實戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞的殘存兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可以輕易殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,其中最大的功臣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪尼·安巴薩 全仗你的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝你不在的這段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好好珍惜我的恭維
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,卡巴迦裏是昆達拉守護神的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是昆達拉的靈魂安息地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,卡巴的守護神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,正確稱呼是迦裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,和這架機體很配
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,吉特團真是多產呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,昆和契卡拉什麼都往船上塞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,來地球一路沒閒過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,為維護？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,從組裝開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,多簡潔的外形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉 你確認…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要用Bifron做靶機嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,它已經接近極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,讓駕駛員親手了結
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎都很嚮往軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你們見過金星殖民圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,過分和平就會產生那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉 戴面具的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我因為有瑪尼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,才有了戰鬥的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這次瑪尼失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我深深體會到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,願意聽聽我的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,和貝魯利做朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他是個仰仗母親家世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,注定邁上仕途的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,結識亞美利亞監軍的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他遲早會成為獨裁者！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達和貝魯利是姐弟！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他們出生於托瓦薩格的雷哈頓家族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嬰兒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就被安排逃亡地球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,能駕駛G-Self 是最好的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那如果是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,豈不是更純正的貴族血統？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,天生被人吃的昆達拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在那些人看來連蟲子也不如！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,導向護罩 良好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bifron會如何進攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管這些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,說到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,到底什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是在胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是測試機動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到它這麼機敏吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 剛才的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看外形絕無法想到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil按預定時間出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是 請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們到過的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只是羅薩裏奧Ⅹ和海桌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不及金星殖民圈的1%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,金星殖民圈的拉古總裁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他穿著奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,總是抱歉 抱歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是位謙虛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,200歲…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,第二站點Hayyan上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,母親和昆珀上校在等您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞艦隊幾時走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,父親說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,發給德瑞特艦隊的停戰協議遲遲得不到回音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以出發 去催促他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,從聖波爾圖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一路打到低軌道的兩支艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可能停戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果歸還神轎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,並非不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,神轎身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看重這些的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,已經成為過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拉古總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,曾這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕宇宙臍帶教和禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,會被人淡忘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,二位的父母 曾憂心忡忡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,您認識他們？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在聖波爾圖聽到類似傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們先告辭了 法皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在那個家庭長大是我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:06:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,法皇的小艇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是去Hayyan嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是難得的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dharma和Dahack
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dharma和Dahack？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,以Dharma為裝甲的機動戰士？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是吉特團那夥人的得意之作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那架Trinity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,給礙事的手腳裝上了武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,說是給我用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,想馬上試駕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,當然越早越好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這就準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你們接回了法皇大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,克裏姆 感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下高興就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有昨日火蠑螈的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我們才能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,把法皇大人順利接回Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這東西看起來真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Gehennam和Hecate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,連續征戰勞損嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒帶慰勞品的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,會恨你一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,米克·傑克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,克裏姆·尼克也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的任性給二位添了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,弦月船帶回的土特產…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,足夠讓人感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我們和亞美利亞艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,上下夾擊Capital軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,逼其就範的這紙作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,相當於半張停戰協議了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞的尼肯寧總統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,已經允許我們移住Capital特區
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這是在和談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,按道理是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但亞美利亞握有神轎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,過早談判會陷入不利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等我為洛克帕報仇以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,再停戰不遲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還在說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,前往拉特爾派森號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們控制著弦月船和神轎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,處於絕對優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼發出停戰協議！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們和德瑞特艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,之所以聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是為對付Capital艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他們經歷過殘酷的宇宙世紀戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不可輕易相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,火蠑螈號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,已經塗裝耐熱塗層
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,去地球也能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,知道麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特艦隊也在休整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,「等降落地球後」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他們也會這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,降落地球後？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,站在德瑞特艦隊的立場？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,到時會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,自己好好想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏已經是軍事基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,請在這邊的房間歇息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,連第二站點Hayyan也要被軍事化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,請諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為將這裏作為最終防線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,此番讓您成為神轎的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,難為您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是一直留在房間中而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,能保護茹甘司令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看得入神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}不許帶進司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}那放在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}美術品放在其他房間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,法皇安全抵達了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,司令為何親自出擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,據說德瑞特和古匈的艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,正打算會合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要親眼確認
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們手中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有直指亞美利亞總統的導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,面具還爭取到滿月船的協助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解戰爭的臨場感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有助指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特艦隊絕不敢動Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 這些好戰的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,無藥可救！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特和亞美利亞艦隊號稱要會合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞握有神轎和弦月船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不信古匈甘願和德瑞特聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,滿月船上的面具上尉還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是去看出好戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯金 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,第二站點的Hayyan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,駛出了Capital軍的戰艦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下 貝魯利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我們之前看到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯金號在做出擊準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯媽媽為什麼不阻止他們？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不妨礙冠艇時刻表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她是不會對軍隊說三道四的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,測試裙甲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,記得做激光校準
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,能拖動強襲背包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不會用到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,遠距離狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只會殺駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,根據戰局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,選擇有效的武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,卡希爾上尉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 貝魯利學員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,單純的牽制攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也是強襲的強項
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,用G-Self的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,用艦橋監視器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,觀察敵人艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好認真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,漂出船外會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,終於打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,雷達癱瘓了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,切換成CG
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,艦隊會合的空域出現米諾夫斯基粒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特和亞美利亞的艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說達成停戰協議了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是這麼期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是CG化的緣故…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,兩支艦隊的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,非常奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這…不是對話的姿態！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,史堤厄 引擎臨界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,無線電癱瘓說明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼近距離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,會打艦隊戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,開火 讓他們開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在炮擊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,會擊落己方機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,亞美利亞艦隊也遲遲不動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,說明米諾夫斯基粒子是第三者所為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,第三者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,第三者在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是滿月船方向嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,準備艦隊戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,機動戰士後撤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,滿月船上有什麼東西起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:14:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,面具那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,米克回防火蠑螈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,天才克裏姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如何解讀當前事態？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不如觀戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯金放出了機動部隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,最大倍率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看熱鬧不嫌事大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,全員 一級戰備待命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,磨磨蹭蹭會變成機動戰士戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,軟體光束 照射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,進入一級戰鬥距離
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,開始空轉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil 開眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,踹開那丫頭 被面具討厭雖然不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,總好過被認為是無能的女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil 為我占卜運勢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,德瑞特和亞美利亞艦隊悉數到場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,現在才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裏來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,滿月船的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,規避運動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,向目標開火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,別被彎曲的光束迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,右舷上方 上方！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,光束扭曲不同尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,消失的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,像顆大樹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是滿月船帶來的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,軟體光束的威力 這裏也能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,還不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,面具上尉的部下 芭拉拉·佩歐茹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,挺有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是位出色的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,把嫉妒帶上戰場會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,看不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,和葛蘭登已經相隔大氣層了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看不見的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yggdrasil的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,加上奇亞隊長和昆達拉的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能營造出不需要金星殖民圈的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然叫滿月船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,它其實只是艘運輸艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這震動是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,相位…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,反轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這不就是軟體光束的缺點麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,後退 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人近在眼前 為什麼不反擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,用強襲攻擊亂向光束的源頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在此之前別去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄準打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:17:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,正中！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,面具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我作為駕駛員是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拿我和那種丫頭相比
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,角度再深
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,被埋伏 還遇到那種光束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,諾頓將軍的幾內比紹號呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,眼下要逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,洛克帕告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？這種時候還…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,地球方向援軍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,光束和導彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,護罩無法堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,軟體光束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止震動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,重啟護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,光束也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 裙甲激光可以作為防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,知道用法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer打開突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer的那個姿勢…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,釋放發振
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,放出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只要衝進懷裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,軟體光束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,全裝裙甲是很亮的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,軟體光束被衝散了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,能用的穿梭機和小艇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,全部載人潛入Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這是臨陣脫逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,艦隊的最終目的是回歸作戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,讓盡可能多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,從Capital塔潛入地球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,求變於未來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,您說求變…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,去到地球願望會脫胎換骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,全員…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Capita…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,幾內比紹號被擊沉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐去保護拉特爾派森上的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,強襲模式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,光束被擋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self的話 Yggdrasil！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Copy-Paste盾 能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,摧毀整整一支艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,意味著什麼 明白嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,芭拉拉·佩歐茹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,請穿上太空服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,金字塔的敵人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,正在制服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 離開空域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,碎片太多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,到處是德瑞特和亞美利亞的殘部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這片碎片帶正在向滿月船靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.08,0:21:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近 靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 要哭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,回去再哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,父親他…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真的相信著停戰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,復原出那種東西的金星殖民圈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,面具和那裏的滿月船會合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出了那種兵器
